flowchart TD
    A[Search request] --> B[SearchController]
    B --> C[Search backend registry]
    C --> D[ElasticsearchBackend]
    C --> P[PgSearchBackend]
    D --> E[Elasticsearch query execution]
    P --> Q[pg_search scope execution]
    P --> R[SQL-backed match scoring]
    Q --> R
    E --> F[Search results returned]
    R --> F
    F --> G[TrackSearchQueryJob]
    G --> H[SearchQueryCaptureService]
    H --> I{Platform analytics mode}
    I -- disabled --> J[Do not persist query text]
    I -- hashed --> K[Persist sha256 query digest]
    I -- full --> L[Persist normalized query text]
    D --> M[Live validation and audit-oriented specs]
    P --> N[Integration specs with pg_search scopes]
